doc.title: programmearring
doc.description: Dit diel giet oer hoe't jo programmearje

example1.title: {{0}}Thússidekoade foarbyld
example1.annotation1: Bepale oft it deselde primêre domeinnamme is.
example1.annotation2: Bepale of it is {{0}} of de thússide fan it kanaal begjint mei it @-symboal As dat sa is, werom {{1}}.
example1.annotation3: Bepale oft it in fideoside is. It paad begjint mei /watch.
example1.annotation4: Bepale oft it in koarte fideoside is. It paad begjint mei /shorts/.
example1.annotation5: Bepale oft it in postside is. It paad begjint mei /post/.
